==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
βάθος / bathos / bath'-os

===Etymology===

From the same as  [[βαθύς]] {{GG|901}}

===Noun===
'''βάθος'''

# profundity, that is, (by implication) extent; (figuratively) mystery: - [[deep]] (-ness, things), [[depth]].

